Spain’s Seized Lender CAM to Cut 973 Jobs, Europa Press Says

-- B y   E s t e b a n   D u a r t e
-- 
2011-10-23T11:55:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/spain-s-seized-lender-cam-to-cut-973-jobs-europa-press-says.html
Spain ’s bank-rescue fund plans to
cut 973 jobs from  Caja de Ahorros del Mediterraneo (CAM)  as part of a
restructuring of the seized lender,  Europa Press  reported,
citing unidentified people familiar with the process.  The FROB, as the fund is known, will complete its
restructuring of the savings bank by Dec. 15, the news agency
said. Most of the job cuts will be carried out through early
retirements, Europa Press said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Esteban Duarte in Madrid at 
 eduarterubia@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
